                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "The spectacles key in on someone to show you their social cues in perfect clarity. Choose a creature you can see. You gain a +3 item bonus on Perception checks you make to use Sense Motive against that creature. This benefit lasts until you Activate the item again in this way. If you\u2019re an investigator, you can use this activation as part of the Devise a Stratagem action (even if you\u2019re doing it as a free action). Alternatively, you can use it as part of the Pursue a Lead activity, even though you can\u2019t see the creature. You must choose the same creature you chose for Devise a Stratagem or Pursue a Lead.",
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "Sense Motive",
                            "alt": "Sense Motive",
